    <thetext>BETA_JAVA8:

The following program should fail to compile, but compiles successfully:

// ----
interface I {
	void foo(X x);
}

public class X {
	void foo() {
	}
	
	public void main(String[] args) {
		I i = @Marker X::foo;
	}
}


The compiler silently acepts the undefined annotation Marker</thetext>
